headline: Ulta Beauty price target raised to $476 from $442 at Canaccord
summary: Canaccord raised the firm’s price target on Ulta Beauty (ULTA) to $476 from $442 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm said heading into earnings they are becoming more positive on the company as they believe Sephora’s store openings have continued to slow and Ulta promos have been fairly rational and just incrementally higher versus last year.
